      <div class="container text-center mb-5">
        <h1>About Harvest Horizon</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Harvest Horizon is a website that utilizes machine learning features
          to help farmers stay up-to-date with the latest agricultural trends
          and manage their expenses more efficiently. Our platform offers
          insights into crop predictions, weather forecasts, and much more to
          ensure farmers can make informed decisions for a better harvest. By
          combining the power of AI with real-time data, we aim to empower
          farmers and revolutionize farming practices. The goal of Harvest
          Horizon is to be the one-stop solution for every farmer, providing
          them with tools to maximize their productivity, minimize their costs,
          and stay ahead of market trends. Whether you're looking for crop
          recommendations based on soil conditions or the weather forecast for
          your region, Harvest Horizon is here to assist.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

